"Change Set:		9511MorphicExtras-ar.77MorphicExtras-ar.77:Cleanup for CommandHistory, PaintBoxMorph, PartsBin, and TextOnCurve.MorphicExtras-ar.76:Add TextOnCurve reset to flush some state that will otherwise just hang around."!!CommandHistory class methodsFor: 'class initialization' stamp: 'ar 2/26/2010 23:02'!cleanUp	"Dump command histories"	self resetAllHistory! !!PaintBoxMorph class methodsFor: 'class initialization' stamp: 'ar 2/26/2010 23:03'!cleanUp	"Flush caches"	ColorChart := nil.! !!TextOnCurve class methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 2/26/2010 18:28'!reset	"TextOnCurve reset"	CachedWarpMap := CachedWarpDepth := CachedWarpColor := nil! !!TextOnCurve class methodsFor: 'class initialization' stamp: 'ar 2/26/2010 23:06'!cleanUp	"Flush caches"	self reset.! !!PartsBin class methodsFor: 'class initialization' stamp: 'ar 2/26/2010 23:03'!cleanUp	"Flush caches"	self clearThumbnailCache! !